{"tid":834150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[水桶陣]西九站黃雨下多處漏水　馬時亨視察無回應","createTime":"2018-09-24T04:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T16:53:42.000Z","uid":48083,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"9148e8ba157f030631b3bf82c49df6927bb0023b","tid":834150,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180924/s00001/60f54227d6b523778b4f998df127f746.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F60f54227d6b523778b4f998df127f746.jpg&h=8ef76dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180924/s00001/60f28817a423c3536883b3be849d2e44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F60f28817a423c3536883b3be849d2e44.jpg&h=3264b330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180924/s00001/60f687d3dbdae7e6fcd7d6a89ccafc96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F60f687d3dbdae7e6fcd7d6a89ccafc96.jpg&h=2fd18e87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180924/s00001/60f3de46d31085fa04b97caf3c4fe4a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F60f3de46d31085fa04b97caf3c4fe4a6.jpg&h=8e21a88f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180924/s00001/60f7b35aa2022ba6d0c2355085dfa78c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F60f7b35aa2022ba6d0c2355085dfa78c.jpg&h=26aaa700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港段通車第二日，天文台發出黃雨警告，西九總站多處出現漏水。港鐵主席馬時亨到場觀察漏水情況，但未有回應提問。<br />\n<br />\n黃雨下，西九總站多處漏水。在B2離境大堂的「堂前食坊」內有大攤積水，更不停有水從天幕滴下，水花四濺，其後職員到場拖走積水。<br />\n<br />\n在B1層的食肆門口，擺放了多個水桶接載天幕滴下的水。該層對上的室內平台，亦有多處積水。<br />\n<br />\n在西九總站接駁往西九巴士總站的天橋位置，雨水不停流下，要用6個水桶裝載。<br />\n<br />\n馬時亨今早曾在站內視察。他到B2層「堂前食坊」看過積水，又到洗手間觀察，但未有回應提問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537761034160?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537761034160%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=PDhiVWoQ4brW0VOu49aGq26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b3fb4df3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180924%2Fs00001%2F1537761034160%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=2e7b17ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180924/s00001/1537761034160?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"802a4543075a62c28f64ff495bbf4ca11b2bce04","tid":834150,"uid":192189,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:13:23.000Z","msg":"西撚利,,<br />\n新起第二日就漏水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e57c74c79cd8d702f9ed8be44dbb1bb08cdf03a","tid":834150,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"之前山竹都無出過黎睇其他站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30548bcdd6254f7a5a967134d78320e3f536a635","tid":834150,"uid":91685,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"黃雨已經漏到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88567fba76140ab70ca15460600cf225315d45ae","tid":834150,"uid":10671,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:17:51.000Z","msg":"我話OK就OK啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0542320ebb922d4e13815e86905f6dd828cb10","tid":834150,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"越諗越應該叫多d廢老，同支那蝗去搭， 如果唔係庫房筆維修費好重皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e71e5205c806bfb6497db6e6576f54bc62ac8d2","tid":834150,"uid":19218,"l